data.name: IntroductionLabel.Text
data.value:
Welcome to the Data Folder Creator!
Over here, you can create a custom Data Folder to store your Scripts, Configuration, Maps and more!
To start, input the name of your Data Folder in the box under this text. If you want to see what other options you can change, check the other tabs at the top.
If you plan to create folders with the same options in the future, click save so you can load them when you create the next Data Folder.
Once you are pleased with the settings, click Create at the bottom.
